title: ABBYY PDF Transformer+ 12.0.104.167 Multilang
description:
ABBYY PDF Transformer+ is a powerful tool that enables you to author and to convert PDF files into multiple editable formats. The program is packed with a lot of features that anyone that works with PDF files can find useful.The most basic action that the program can perform is to create a PDF file from a text document. The program can load TXT, RTF or HTML files and transform them in a PDF file in a couple of clicks. But we have to mention that the HTML files will include the images and styes of the original page, not just the text.

Home Page www.abbyy.ru
Language: Multi
